data.description: Nice home in a well established, desirable neighborhood on .35 acres. Located in a secluded cove right around the corner from Terry Park. Unique property- walk through your back gate to Lake Ray Hubbard! Enjoy fishing, ride your 4 wheeler and experience the relaxing days and evenings you have been waiting for. Wake up and sip coffee on the large back patio while enjoying the peace and quiet. Highly desirable Rockwall ISD and also located in Rockwall County. Home needs clean up, paint and flooring. Buyer to verify all information. No HOA.
